      • intercept

        ClientServiceDescriptor.Rules intercept​(int priority,
                                        io.grpc.ClientInterceptor... interceptors)
        Add one or more ClientInterceptor instances that will intercept calls to this service.

        The added interceptors will be applied using the specified priority.

        Parameters:
        priority - the priority to assign to the interceptors
        interceptors - one or more ClientInterceptors to add
        Returns:
        this builder to allow fluent method chaining
